CEO KO JOONG SEOK: If you get this right, I'll...

2066
01:05:40,000 --> 01:05:40,736
HYUNJUN: Money?

2067
01:05:40,736 --> 01:05:41,504
DANIEL: Money, money?

2068
01:05:41,600 --> 01:05:42,200
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: If you get it right...

2069
01:05:42,200 --> 01:05:44,100
(Brightening up at the mention of money)

2070
01:05:44,192 --> 01:05:46,200
(Even the dazed JAEWON snaps to attention)
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: It's two words.

2071
01:05:46,200 --> 01:05:47,200
