2072
01:05:47,200 --> 01:05:48,320
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: He said, "Something is..."

2073
01:05:48,320 --> 01:05:51,936
(Something is one of the world's eight great wonders
and humanity's greatest invention. Albert Einstein)

2074
01:05:51,936 --> 01:05:54,900
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Greatest invention.

2075
01:05:54,900 --> 01:05:57,166
(What does something stand for here?)

2076
01:05:57,166 --> 01:05:58,688
(A very important point from today's lesson)
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Because it's so important.

2077
01:05:58,752 --> 01:06:00,133
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: It's today's highlight.

2078
01:06:00,133 --> 01:06:00,864
DANIEL: Banknotes!

2079
01:06:01,120 --> 01:06:01,664
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Banknotes?

2080
01:06:01,664 --> 01:06:02,304
DANIEL: Currency.

2081
01:06:02,464 --> 01:06:03,776
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Let me give you a hint.

2082
01:06:03,776 --> 01:06:04,768
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: It's about interest rates.

2083
01:06:04,768 --> 01:06:06,533
(The hint is a word related to interest rate)
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: It's related to interest rate.

2084
01:06:06,533 --> 01:06:07,424
DANIEL: Bank.

2085
