CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Bank interest!

2087
01:06:09,376 --> 01:06:11,100
DANIEL: Ah, I thought I'd gotten the answer right.

2088
01:06:11,100 --> 01:06:12,466
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: It's that type of interest.

2089
01:06:12,466 --> 01:06:14,366
