CEO KO JOONG SEOK: Of course, of course.

2243
01:10:54,144 --> 01:10:56,366
- CEO KO JOONG SEOK: I saw it.
- DANIEL: Did it shine?

2244
01:10:56,366 --> 01:10:57,568
CEO KO JOONG SEOK: You're completely different.

2245
01:10:58,200 --> 01:11:01,400
- CEO KO JOONG SEOK: You're people who shine just by existing.
- TRAINEE: Thank you.

2246
