01:26:39,264 --> 01:26:40,733
SONGHA: Time was really short.

2699
01:26:41,266 --> 01:26:42,933
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: This is
actually all the time you get.

2700
01:26:42,933 --> 01:26:44,416
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: At a real
fan signing, it's really like this.

2701
01:26:44,416 --> 01:26:45,792
HANBI: It was really short.

2702
01:26:46,099 --> 01:26:47,264
(To fans, it's such precious time)
HARUTA: Hello.

2703
01:26:47,296 --> 01:26:48,320
NA PD: Hello.

2704
01:26:49,064 --> 01:26:50,464
HARUTA: I really enjoyed watching

2705
01:26:50,566 --> 01:26:52,733
HARUTA: the 'Game Caterers' episode with the seniors.

2706
01:26:52,966 --> 01:26:55,599
(Because CHANGMIN appeared)

2707
01:26:55,799 --> 01:26:56,933
HARUTA: I enjoyed it.

2708
01:26:57,024 --> 01:26:57,824
NA PD: What's your name?

2709
01:26:57,824 --> 01:26:58,752
(HARUTA self-introduction)
HARUTA: I'm HARUTA.

2710
01:26:58,976 --> 01:27:00,133
NA PD: To HARUTA.

2711
01:27:00,233 --> 01:27:01,766
HARUTA: I'm nervous!

2712
01:27:02,560 --> 01:27:05,024
NA PD: Why are you nervous, don't be.
No need to be nervous.

2713
01:27:05,024 --> 01:27:06,144
HANBI: Ah, so this is how it feels.

2714
01:27:08,256 --> 01:27:10,208
(So much to realize)
NA PD: One minute is really this short?

2715
01:27:11,599 --> 01:27:12,999
NA PD: HARUTA, you are handsome.

2716
01:27:12,999 --> 01:27:13,999
HARUTA: Thank you.

2717
01:27:14,166 --> 01:27:15,399
(Time's up)

2718
01:27:15,399 --> 01:27:17,433
(NA PD's fan signing ends!)
HARUTA: Thank you.

2719
01:27:18,199 --> 01:27:19,933
(Tidying up)

2720
01:27:20,299 --> 01:27:22,399
(Now is the time to part)
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: We'll wrap up the fan signing practice.

2721
01:27:22,399 --> 01:27:23,104
NA PD: Bye.

2722
01:27:23,104 --> 01:27:24,799
(Loud and cheerful farewell)
ALL: Thank you!

2723
01:27:24,799 --> 01:27:27,299
NA PD: Really nice to see you.

2724
01:27:27,566 --> 01:27:28,699
NA PD: Wrap things up well.

2725
01:27:28,699 --> 01:27:30,099
NA PD: Do well with your debut,
so we can meet again!

2726
01:27:30,099 --> 01:27:31,872
(Let's meet again)
- SONGHA: Yes, thank you so much. - JUSTIN: Thank you.

2727
01:27:32,288 --> 01:27:33,088
NA PD: Bye.

2728
01:27:33,088 --> 01:27:35,840
(NA PD leaves, giving a precious experience)
ALL: Thank you.

2729
01:27:36,288 --> 01:27:37,952
(Zero sense of reality)

2730
01:27:38,496 --> 01:27:39,616
(Fan manager)
STAFF: Should I give you an autograph too?

2731
01:27:39,616 --> 01:27:40,576
SONGHA: Okay!

2732
01:27:42,336 --> 01:27:43,543
- TRAINEE: We're done.
- FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: Good work, everyone.

2733
01:27:43,543 --> 01:27:46,400
(After-school sessions all end)
ALL: Thank you.

2734
01:27:46,533 --> 01:27:48,599
JUSTIN: Is there no photocard of NA PD?

2735
01:27:48,766 --> 01:27:50,666
(Instructor with photocard)
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: Oh, yes, I have one.

2736
01:27:51,616 --> 01:27:52,833
(And thus, becomes a fan collecting photocards)
JUSTIN: I want to receive one.

2737
01:27:53,099 --> 01:27:54,833
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: From now on,
every photocard photo you take

2738
01:27:54,833 --> 01:27:55,599
FAN LOVE INSTRUCTOR: will matter.

2739
01:27:57,056 --> 01:27:58,066
HANBI: Definitely.

2740
01:27:58,656 --> 01:28:00,966
(A class better than expected)
SONGHA: The class was really good.

2741
01:28:01,056 --> 01:28:02,266
SONGHA: I really didn't know anything.

2742
01:28:02,266 --> 01:28:02,752
(Not taught anywhere else)
JUSTIN: I didn't know.

2743
01:28:03,008 --> 01:28:03,808
TRAINEE: Nothing to waste, I really didn't know.

2744
01:28:03,808 --> 01:28:04,544
(Stanning)
JUSTIN: That word!

2745
01:28:05,248 --> 01:28:06,499
KASSHO: It's hard.

2746
01:28:06,733 --> 01:28:08,966
HANBI: The fan love lecture was genuinely helpful.

2747
01:28:08,966 --> 01:28:10,848
- HAMIN: Did you really have a class?
- HANBI: A real class.

2748
01:28:10,848 --> 01:28:12,064
HANBI: Well...

2749
01:28:12,064 --> 01:28:13,344
HANBI: I learned a lot.

2750
01:28:15,766 --> 01:28:18,499
(Before long, after the rain, the sky held the sunset)

2751
01:28:19,033 --> 01:28:21,633
(Dorm 202)

2752
01:28:21,833 --> 01:28:23,712
SONGHA: I'll try writing a diary.

2753
01:28:33,533 --> 01:28:36,224
(Slowly reflecting on)

2754
01:28:36,448 --> 01:28:40,366
(today, and myself on today)

2755
01:28:44,512 --> 01:28:47,008
(Life's first photocard)

2756
01:28:48,224 --> 01:28:49,184
(Pre-interview)
SONGHA: I joined this company

2757
01:28:49,184 --> 01:28:51,366
SONGHA: when I was in the first year of middle school.

2758
01:28:51,872 --> 01:28:55,666
SONGHA: Should I describe myself
as a long-term trainee now?

2759
01:28:57,399 --> 01:28:59,066
(At one corner of the dorm)

2760
01:28:59,066 --> 01:29:02,133
(HANBI is writing today's diary)

2761
01:29:04,704 --> 01:29:08,288
(It was first-come, first-served, so I waited early
Attended the 'fan love' class - HANBI)

2762
01:29:08,992 --> 01:29:12,499
(Pre-interview)
HANBI: I've been a trainee at SM for about 6 years now.

2763
01:29:12,499 --> 01:29:14,266
HANBI: In those 6 years,

2764
01:29:14,266 --> 01:29:15,733
HANBI: a lot has happened.

2765
01:29:15,999 --> 01:29:17,533
HANBI: With friends around me,

2766
01:29:17,533 --> 01:29:19,744
HANBI: I endured it together with my trainee friends.

2767
01:29:20,480 --> 01:29:23,296
HANBI: I think I worked hard with one goal in mind.

2768
01:29:25,363 --> 01:29:27,360
SONGHA: Doing it just among us...

2769
01:29:27,575 --> 01:29:29,504
HANBI: Right, it's the last time as SMTR.

2770
01:29:29,536 --> 01:29:32,096
SONGHA: Right, as SMTR, this might be the last time.

2771
01:29:40,736 --> 01:29:44,480
(Even though I'm currently a trainee
without a single photocard - HANBI)

2772
01:29:46,099 --> 01:29:50,166
(If the day comes for me,
I'll fully cherish that love - HANBI)

2773
01:29:50,880 --> 01:29:53,024
(If I debut... - SONGHA)

2774
01:29:54,784 --> 01:29:58,299
(I felt that I really have to give back
as much as the fans give me - SONGHA)

2775
01:29:58,560 --> 01:30:00,576
SONGHA: We don't know

2776
01:30:00,832 --> 01:30:02,848
SONGHA: what will happen to each of us yet,

2777
01:30:03,399 --> 01:30:04,999
SONGHA: but we're

2778
01:30:04,999 --> 01:30:06,633
SONGHA: all running

2779
01:30:06,720 --> 01:30:11,099
SONGHA: toward the same goal of debuting.

2780
01:30:12,699 --> 01:30:18,333
(I don't know yet where the end
of this long race will be)

2781
01:30:20,544 --> 01:30:25,600
(I'm receiving help greater than
what I see in my world)

2782
01:30:25,696 --> 01:30:30,368
(Let's always be grateful - HANBI)

2783
01:30:33,883 --> 01:30:37,472
