(Learning games from Super Junior,)

2804
01:31:20,433 --> 01:31:22,066
(who's been debuting for 22 years)

2805
01:31:22,066 --> 01:31:23,520
KYUHYUN: Ah, we have to show it.

2806
01:31:23,680 --> 01:31:25,533
