KYUHYUN: This is what a true entertainer is.

2807
01:31:26,681 --> 01:31:27,968
(Surpassing the teacher)

2808
01:31:28,736 --> 01:31:30,362
HEECHUL: Brother HANBI.

2809
01:31:30,752 --> 01:31:32,544
(Quickly jokes snap into place)

2810
01:31:33,533 --> 01:31:35,333
