2811
01:31:37,433 --> 01:31:40,899
(An unpredictable sports event is...)

2812
01:31:40,899 --> 01:31:42,080
(Coming up soon)
JAEWON: Na na na boo boo!

2813
01:31:42,080 --> 01:31:43,680
HEECHUL: Na na na boo boo?

2814
01:31:43,680 --> 01:31:44,896
TRAINEE: Na na na boo boo.

2815
01:31:44,957 --> 01:31:45,952
TRAINEE: Na na na boo boo?

2816
01:31:49,568 --> 01:31:55,328
(Ending song,
"Good Person" (feat. Kim Hyung Joong) - Toy)

2817
01:33:15,824 --> 01:33:17,358
TRAINEE: What's up?

2818
01:33:20,282 --> 01:33:21,289
HANBI: Thank you.

2819
01:33:57,133 --> 01:33:58,272
HYUNJUN: I'll go too, then.

2820
01:33:59,232 --> 01:34:00,480
HYUNJUN: Goodbye.

